                                <p>Please do not pay the fee at your current location. On the day of the orientation in NTU CoM,  you will be directed to  the near convnience store and pay the fee either in  Taiwanese dollar or credit card  preferrable)</p>
                                <p><a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-rounded">payment sheet SOP</a></p>
                                <div class="upload-wrapper fluid-wrapper">
                                    <div class="upload-item">
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                              <input class="form-control" type="file" id="academicRecords">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="ft-action">
                                            <span>
                                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Upload</button>
                                            </span>
                                            <span>
                                                <div class="file-pill">
                                                    <a href="#" target="_blank" class="filename" title="避免檔名過長有限制最大寬度.jpg">避免檔名過長有限制最大寬度.jpg</a>
